00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:41,580
=Episode 23=

17
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,760
Li He didn’t make into the final?

18
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,590
We don’t want to believe it, either.

19
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,230
But that’s the truth.

20
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:55,710
We’ve never expected that

21
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:57,560
Li He would lose a competition.

22
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:02,040
Right. It’s as unbelievable as

23
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,590
Zeyu failing an exam.

24
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,200
How’s he doing now?

25
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,360
I’ve never seen Li He act like this.

26
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,190
He’s so horrifyingly silent.

27
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:16,080
Yuan, if only you were there…

28
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,380
My sister was there.

29
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:19,560
She could have watched the race
if she didn’t pass out.

30
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,960
Yuan…!

31
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,900
I’m fine. I just fainted.

32
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:26,360
I just needed some rest.

33
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:28,710
I just don’t get you.

34
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,430
Now is the time you
need each other the most.

35
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,800
But you’re hiding from him
while he’s hiding from you.

36
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,750
The result comes out on Friday.

37
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,710
Wait a bit longer.

38
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:44,590
Yuan, I understand that
you didn’t tell him

39
00:02:44,590 --> 00:02:46,680
because he were to
compete in the race.

40
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,190
But now Li He’s race is over.

41
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,800
You can tell him the truth.

42
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,870
Yuan, do you have any idea

43
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:56,630
how anxious I am being a bystander?

44
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,840
Okay.

45
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,630
I promise you. I’ll tell him
when the result comes out.

46
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,630
Okay, Yuan, so you...

47
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,710
Han Yayi.

48
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,870
Fine. I’ll shut up.

49
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:16,470
Yuan, take care of yourself.

50
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,400
I’ll go now.

51
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:23,430
Come. Have some fruit.

52
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,470
I’ll pass, aunt.

53
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,870
What? You’re leaving?

54
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:28,800
Yes.

55
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,240
You just arrived.

56
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,120
Thank you, aunt.

57
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:36,240
Take some rest.

58
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:37,870
Ah. Okay.

59
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:39,680
Mrs. Yuan, I’ll go now.

60
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,680
You’re both leaving so soon?

61
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,520
Mrs. Yuan, goodbye.

62
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,430
Take it slow.

63
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,750
Only my son wants some fruit.

64
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,520
Here.

65
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,080
Caixi.

66
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:50,590
Yeah?

67
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:51,590
Come. Have some fruit.

68
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:53,400
Oh. I’ll pass. You two enjoy.

69
00:03:58,150 --> 00:03:59,080
What’s going on with your sister?

70
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:33,000
Li He.

71
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,720
Zeyu is here.

72
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:38,190
Zeyu.

73
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:41,240
Look. He has been like this
after the race.

74
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,160
He shuts himself in his room
and he eats nothing.

75
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,510
He ignores us when we talk to him.

76
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,040
Aunt, uncle, don’t worry.

77
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,190
I’ll talk to him.

78
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:50,870
Try to comfort him.

79
