getting up early

681
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:16,400
to take detours every day for two years

682
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,920
so that he can walk to school with you?

683
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:28,760
A few days ago, I watched
the rebroadcast of programming contest.

684
00:38:29,230 --> 00:38:30,190
Zeyu didn’t compete in it.

685
00:38:33,070 --> 00:38:34,320
That day

686
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,320
was also the day of Li He’s semi-final.

687
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,510
Think about it yourself.

688
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:42,150
Will you still go out with him today?

689
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,280
I think to keep going on like this

690
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:47,480
will not do anyone any good.

691
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,400
You’re right.

692
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:58,110
I’ll talk to Zeyu.

693
00:39:13,150 --> 00:39:14,000
Let’s go.

694
00:39:15,550 --> 00:39:16,230
Okay.

695
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:20,360
My sister is like a piece of hardwood.

696
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:24,440
Only a burning flame like Li He
can light her.

697
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:27,960
Warm water like you

698
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,670
