699
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:41,110
Are you hungry?
Shall we grab some food first?

700
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:43,630
I’m indeed a little hungry.

701
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:48,960
Come with me.

702
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:49,470
Mmm?

703
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:58,880
(Yuan’s Fried Chicken)

704
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,510
I often came here before.

705
00:40:02,190 --> 00:40:03,360
Good for you.

706
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:04,580
I didn’t see this side of you.

707
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,840
I thought you

708
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:06,960
eat books only.

709
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:11,070
That would be quite repulsive.

710
00:40:12,510 --> 00:40:15,550
In the past, when my mom and dad
went to the court,

711
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:17,440
I would eat at this place
when I got the chance.

712
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:19,140
The set meal of fried chickens,
coke, and French fries

713
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:20,280
really brought me so much joy.

714
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:22,070
So you have hidden personalities.

715
00:40:23,590 --> 00:40:25,670
There are many sides of me
that are still unknown to you.

716
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:30,110
Excuse me. Here’s the food you ordered.
Please enjoy.

717
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:31,510
-Okay. Thanks.
-Thanks.

718
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:35,010
Listen.

719
00:40:35,010 --> 00:40:37,550
Their fried chicken is so good with…

720
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:38,840
With pepper salt.

721
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:42,190
You had it before?

722
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:43,920
Yes. Li He took me here once.

723
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,760
He also made a joke. This restaurant…

724
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:57,880
-Is called Yuan’s, right?
-Mmm.

725
00:41:02,670 --> 00:41:03,480
Mmm.

726
00:41:19,590 --> 00:41:20,960
Let’s go straight to the show.

727
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:22,670
It’s still too early.

728
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:24,070
Let me take you to an interesting place.

729
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,510
Ah!

730
00:41:25,510 --> 00:41:26,630
Yep. Let’s go.

731
00:41:29,220 --> 00:41:32,400
(Simon Tree Baking Class
Parent-kid bakery)

732
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,190
This way.

733
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,710
Wait a second.

734
00:41:40,710 --> 00:41:42,000
You took me here to make a cake?

735
00:41:42,230 --> 00:41:44,400
Yes. Li He must have never
brought you here.

736
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,320
No. I can’t imagine

737
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:50,800
he brings me here to make a cake.

738
00:41:51,550 --> 00:41:53,110
But I also can’t imagine

739
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:54,760
you bring me here to make a cake.

740
00:41:55,670 --> 00:41:57,440
I told you there are many sides of me

741
00:41:57,440 --> 00:41:58,550
that you still don’t know.

742
00:41:58,920 --> 00:41:59,710
Come on.

743
00:42:00,710 --> 00:42:01,330
Hello, everyone.

744
00:42:01,330 --> 00:42:03,320
Today, in our class,

745
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:04,960
we’ll make a Chiffon Cake.

746
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,320
Chiffon Cake is one of

747
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:08,670
the four major cakes in bakery.

748
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:14,310
♪The distance between us♪

749
00:42:14,310 --> 00:42:16,870
♪Changes all the time♪

750
00:42:17,630 --> 00:42:19,810
♪Just like the last dessert♪

751
00:42:19,930 --> 00:42:23,010
♪Making me want more♪

752
00:42:23,540 --> 00:42:25,560
♪I don’t dare to breathe anymore♪

753
00:42:25,690 --> 00:42:28,060
♪In case you feel my heart♪

754
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:32,490
♪Turn my back to you with courage♪

755
