♪Oh my dear you♪

756
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:39,410
♪This is my love letter♪

757
00:42:39,510 --> 00:42:40,530
♪No words♪

758
00:42:40,530 --> 00:42:43,980
♪Can express my feelings enough♪

759
00:42:45,250 --> 00:42:48,190
♪How I wish♪

760
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:50,660
♪I could get closer to you♪

761
00:42:50,770 --> 00:42:52,960
♪Why don’t we be together♪

762
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:55,140
♪Just you and me♪

763
00:43:08,190 --> 00:43:09,190
Well done.

764
00:43:10,480 --> 00:43:11,280
Just so-so.

765
00:43:14,230 --> 00:43:17,030
