how to make a Chiffon Cake.”

771
00:43:28,070 --> 00:43:29,550
But I couldn’t read it right back then.

772
00:43:29,550 --> 00:43:31,280
So I would mistake “Chiffon”

773
00:43:31,280 --> 00:43:32,400
