774
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:34,590
When I was in third grade
of primary school,

775
00:43:34,590 --> 00:43:36,190
I once made a cake for my mom,
and I said,

776
00:43:36,550 --> 00:43:38,190
“Mom, eat this Chicken Cake,

777
00:43:38,190 --> 00:43:40,070
and it’ll be a piece a cake for you
in the court.”

778
00:43:42,530 --> 00:43:47,200
♪Unsure of our relationship♪

779
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:53,070
♪Lack of courage to approach♪

780
00:43:53,670 --> 00:43:54,480
Done.

781
00:43:55,110 --> 00:43:55,920
Good job.

782
00:43:55,920 --> 00:43:56,590
Not bad, huh?

783
00:43:56,590 --> 00:43:59,030
♪The text tells the words
I dare not say♪

784
00:43:59,190 --> 00:44:01,760
