♪Oh my dear you♪

787
00:44:06,470 --> 00:44:09,810
♪This is my love letter♪

788
00:44:09,810 --> 00:44:10,770
♪No words♪

789
00:44:10,770 --> 00:44:14,270
♪Can express my feelings enough♪

