793
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:22,760
It’s time to go to the tech expo.

794
00:44:22,760 --> 00:44:23,280
Okay.

795
00:44:23,500 --> 00:44:26,090
♪Just you and me♪

796
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:45,840
Good job, kid.

797
00:44:45,840 --> 00:44:47,000
You’re as good as your old time now.

798
00:44:47,960 --> 00:44:48,840
