on that day of the race.

802
00:44:55,590 --> 00:44:56,550
There will be more races.

803
00:44:56,960 --> 00:44:58,110
I will win next time.

804
00:44:58,510 --> 00:45:00,550
Good, kiddo. This is the right attitude.

805
00:45:00,550 --> 00:45:01,800
You’re also in the right mentality.

806
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:02,920
You taught me well.

807
00:45:03,800 --> 00:45:05,670
Save it. Practice shuttle run later.

808
00:45:06,070 --> 00:45:06,760
Okay.

