814
00:45:44,230 --> 00:45:46,920
Its name is Unimate.

815
00:45:55,400 --> 00:45:56,110
Isn’t this fun?

816
00:45:56,110 --> 00:45:57,150
They’re so synchronized.

817
00:45:57,670 --> 00:45:58,360
Yep.

818
